org.dolan.searcher

Class Searcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dolan.searcher.Searcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISearcher

    public class Searcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISearcher
    The Class Searcher. This is an implementation of ISearcher. It is the core of the application. It searches a file up and down and returns results based on the Regex query.
